ttps://x.com/yoshibanakokoro" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Kokoro Yoshihana</strong></a>和<a href="https://x.com/itopoid" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Itopoid</strong></a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp" width="1024" height="576" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.vgewi5id23p2-jpg.webp 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" ></a></p><p>在 Hakotore V 中，您可以通过将自己和 VTuber 叠加在镜面显示屏上来进行训练，从而轻松有趣地学习正确的姿势。此外，担任教练的VTuber的声音全部是新录制的。</p><p>此外，动作捕捉摄像头会检测玩家的动作，VTuber 会匹配玩家的节奏。菜单由热爱肌肉训练的VTuber和训练教练全程监督，设计涵盖了从初学者到资深用户、从有氧运动到高强度训练的所有内容。它还具有可以在SNS上发布的纪念照片功能，提供VTuber和粉丝在同一空间一起享受运动的体验。</p><h2>参与VTuber评论</h2><h3>初级教练：舞鹤洋加人</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp" alt="" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-254021" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-768x768.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.29dfuukmalt-jpg.webp 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p><p>嘿！我是横藤舞鹤，出生于福冈县福冈市中央区舞鹤的虚拟博多女孩！<br />横门真的很喜欢福冈，经常让大家知道福冈的美食、好玩的活动、美丽的地方等等！<br />横藤舞鹤有时被称为博多大猩猩或肉体鬼，但有时她的肌肉训练跟不上，所以希望她和大家一起努力！ ！ ！让我们一起离健康更近一些！ ！ ！</p><p> YouTube： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@maizuruyokato" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/@maizuruyokato</a><br /> X： <a href="https://x.com/yokato_ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://x.com/yokato_ch</a></p><h3>中级教练：吉香心</h3><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-300x300.webp" alt="" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-254022" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-768x768.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/e420e8fab0c5aa2a49078d1b72f374d0-kix.csmosbnmhqga-jpg.webp 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p><p>我是吉花心，来自千叶县的狼VTuber，据说只是“看起来不会运动”！<br />我平时给大家发ASMR视频的主题是“透明治愈放松”，但其实我是一只从小在空手道、网球、篮球、田径上挥汗如雨的超强狼。我爱追！<br />事实上，由于进行过多的肌肉训练对我的身体造成压力，我什至让医生停下来。虽然我的身体能力和潜力未知，但正是因为我的身体受过一次伤，我才敏锐地意识到首先学习“正确训练”的重要性。<br />这个夏天，何不走出房间，和Hakotore V一起打造健康的身体呢？<br />我想尽全力去见我所爱的每一个人，尽可能久一点，哪怕只有一分钟……！ ！</p><p> YouTube： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Kokoro_Ch" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.youtube.com/@Kokoro_Ch</a><br /> X： <a href="https://x.com/yoshibanakokoro" target="