五弹性歌曲MV发行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-1022x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1022px) 100vw, 1022px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-1022x1024.webp 1022w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-768x769.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/07/17953a3d3f959b88e4c4b6a52eec9b0c-kix.bq32clu711u0-jpg.webp 1348w" width="1022" height="1024" /></a></p><p>东京音乐与舞蹈高中学院（TSM）是一个虚拟偶像项目“ <a href="https://www.so-on-project.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">So.On Project Lav</a> ”，已发布了第五次子弹歌曲“ Connect The Smile”的音乐视频。</p><p>音乐视频包括各种元素，例如受“蝴蝶”和“ Connect”启发的舞蹈场景，这是成员的生活方式，偶像的轨迹以及过去发行的剪裁。</p><p> “ Connect the Smile”已被确定为“ 2024夏季虚拟市场”的认证歌曲。</p><p><a href="https://linkco.re/N36xDuDd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处，</a>以获取“连接微笑”的各种分发目的地。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="So.ON项目LAV第五单曲“ Connect the Smile”音乐视频" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AiV8OF9bc28?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000120.000041195.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">学校公司Jikei Gakuen东京音乐与舞蹈学院新闻稿</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-daily-2024-07-09/">Nijisanji Ventlz/Idol Master Sidem Collaboration Live Decies